July 23, 2017 11:31 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Pitcairn Financial Group



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Pitcairn Financial Group is a privately owned multi-family office. The firm also provides comprehensive planning, investment advisory, estate and tax-planning services. The firm provides its services to multi-generational families. It operates as a subsidiary of Pitcairn Group L P. Pitcairn Financial Group was founded in 1923 and is based in Jenkintown, Pennsylvania with additional offices in Washington, New York City and McLean, Virginia.


One Pitcairn Place165 Township Line RoadSuite 3000Jenkintown, PA 19046-3593United StatesFounded in 1923



Phone: 215-887-6700

Fax: 215-881-6090

www.pitcairn.com







